Nikon El Maestro (born 3 June 1993 as Nikon Jevtić) is a retired Serbian-English footballer who played as an attacking midfielder. 
He played in the youth teams of West Ham, Austria Wien, Valencia and Schalke 04. He was the captain of FK Austria Wien U17 Academy teams in the BNZ (National Youth Austrian League).In March 2014, he took over as head coach of FC Hellas Kagran U11, later taking over as the head coach of the U16 side.
